{
  "message": "test(conformance): add FFT adversarial cases (+12)\n\nFFT adversarial edge cases (12 cases):\n- fft_empty_input: zero-length array handling\n- fft_single_element: trivial transform case\n- fft_with_nan_input: NaN propagation behavior\n- fft_with_inf_input: Infinity handling\n- fft_n_larger_than_input: zero-padding behavior\n- fft_n_smaller_than_input: truncation behavior\n- fft_n_equals_one: minimal n parameter\n- fft_all_zeros: degenerate input\n- fft_alternating_sign: Nyquist frequency peak\n- fft_prime_length: Bluestein algorithm fallback\n- ifft_empty_input: inverse empty handling\n- rfft_odd_length: real FFT odd-length hermitian\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
